net.minecraftforge.fml.event.IModBusEvent
public class RegisterNamedRenderTypesEvent extends net.minecraftforge.eventbus.api.Event implements net.minecraftforge.fml.event.IModBusEvent
Allows users to register custom named render types.

This event is not cancellable, and does not have a result.

This event is fired on the mod-specific event bus, only on the logical client.

    • register

      public void register(String name, RenderType blockRenderType, RenderType entityRenderType, RenderType fabulousEntityRenderType)
      Registers a named RenderTypeGroup.
      参数:
      name - The name
      blockRenderType - One of the values returned by RenderType.chunkBufferLayers()
      entityRenderType - A RenderType using DefaultVertexFormat.NEW_ENTITY
      fabulousEntityRenderType - A RenderType using DefaultVertexFormat.NEW_ENTITY for use when "fabulous" rendering is enabled
